////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

	Cerberus 5 Rotation Manager
    Plugin ID: net.pixelinstrument.rotation_manager
	Licence: GPLv3 http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.txt

////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

The plugin provides 3 scheduler tasks that allow to:

- automatically assign incoming tickets based on defined rotation schemes
- send out a report of open tickets to the workers
- automatically alert workers when tickets are not updated and close them

=== INSTALLATION ===
- install and configure Cerberus Help Desk 5 (http://www.cerberusweb.com)
- download the code in <Cerb5>/features/net.pixelinstrument.rotation_manager
- activate the plugin under setup | Plugins & Features
